column5: Took a greenhorn icefishing yesterday in the big lake.  Caught all the action on film.
Looks great Rob. Hope you have left few for me ha ha ha... Left you a voice mail... Cheers,  Ice Fisherman
Haven't seen a video report from you in a while.... Awesome fishing and some great fish to boot   Congrats to the greenhorn Quality fish and time spent on the hard surface Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice going!    It was a grind out there for me today. 20 miles on the sled 20 holes and only 2 small lakers to show for it... Second guessing where i should start tomorrow
Glad i wasn't the only one!  We only iced one fish and had a few hits!
The past vids have been awesome.  Great job guys.
Excellent video Rob.  Gets me all excited
Dude this video was epic... Loved watching it, great tips, great fishing and fun to watch!!!    WELL DONE
Great video.  Thanks for posting it.
